'''TOML''' 是一种旨在成为一个小规模、易于使用的语义化的[[配置文件格式|配置文件格式]]，<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://mlworks.cn/posts/introduction-to-toml/|title=TOML 简介|accessdate=2017-02-12|author=Ryan Zhao|date=2015-03-03|publisher=|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170402215020/http://mlworks.cn/posts/introduction-to-toml/|archivedate=2017-04-02}}</ref>它被设计为可以无二义性的转换为一个[[哈希表|哈希表]]。

“TOML”这个名字是“Tom's Obvious, Minimal Language（汤姆的浅显的、极简的语言）”的首字母略写词<ref>{{cite web|url=https://github.com/toml-lang/toml#toml|title=toml-lang github|accessdate=2017-02-12|archive-date=2017-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170215183959/https://github.com/toml-lang/toml#toml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。“Tom”指它的作者[[Tom_Preston-Werner|Tom Preston-Werner]]。

TOML已在一些软件工程中使用，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://github.com/toml-lang/toml#projects-using-toml|title=projects using toml|accessdate=2017-02-12|archive-date=2017-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170215183959/https://github.com/toml-lang/toml#projects-using-toml|dead-url=no}}</ref>并且很多[[编程语言|编程语言]]都支持TOML格式数据的解析。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://github.com/toml-lang/toml#implementations|title=toml implementations|accessdate=2017-02-12|archive-date=2017-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170215183959/https://github.com/toml-lang/toml#implementations|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://doc.crates.io/manifest.html|title=cargo config|accessdate=2017-02-12|archive-date=2017-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170130014541/http://doc.crates.io/manifest.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 语法 ==
TOML的语法广泛地由key = "value"、[节名]与#注释构成。

它支持以下数据类型：字符串、整形、浮点型、布尔型、日期时间、数组和图表。

=== 範例 ===
<syntaxhighlight lang=ini>
# 這是一份 TOML 文件

title = "TOML 範例"

[owner]
name = "Tom Preston-Werner"
dob = 1979-05-27T07:32:00-08:00 # First class dates

[database]
server = "192.168.1.1"
ports = [ 8001, 8001, 8002 ]
connection_max = 5000
enabled = true

[servers]

  # 可以使用縮排（TAB或是空格），但不是必要的
  [servers.alpha]
  ip = "10.0.0.1"
  dc = "eqdc10"

  [servers.beta]
  ip = "10.0.0.2"
  dc = "eqdc10"

[clients]
data = [ ["gamma", "delta"], [1, 2] ]

# 可以在陣列中換行
hosts = [
  "alpha",
  "omega"
]
</syntaxhighlight>

